      "Text": "Security update for cockpit",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for cockpit fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-25547: brace-expansion: unbounded brace range expansion can lead to excessive resource consumption and crash\n  a Node.js process (bsc#1257836).\n- CVE-2026-26996: minimatch: processing of glob pattern containing repeated wildcards followed by a literal character\n  that doesn't appear in the test string can lead to ReDoS (bsc#1258641).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
